Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.63,0:00:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.47,0:00:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.27,0:01:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba boy, if you can defeat me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will release Mokuba boy's\N soul from the sealed card.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.75,0:01:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That card has 3000 Attack Points, and it is your most trusted card.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.50,0:01:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragon!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impossible!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did Pegasus see my hand somehow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.78,0:01:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(319,139)}Kaiba Falls!\NThe Invincible Toon World
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.13,0:01:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That power...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus is reading Kaiba-kun's mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.63,0:01:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi oi, if that is true, doesn't that mean it's impossible to defeat that bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.70,0:02:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, It's the power of his Millennium Eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there must be a way to defeat Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn you, Pegasus.... are you really reading my mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.63,0:02:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}None of the cards in my hand can beat Dark Rabbit...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.53,0:02:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play another card in Defense Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.40,0:02:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kaiba boy... do you like cartoons?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? It seems you don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.76,0:02:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I {\i1}love{\i0} them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.95,0:02:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a boy, I used to watch "Funny Rabbit" all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:03:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All those great characters running on the TV were the {\b1}best{\b0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During those days, they were like my best friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To this day, they still run around in the little garden in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will never betray me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they can never die...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.87,0:03:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll invite you to their world!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toon World!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toon World?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.33,0:03:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.80,0:03:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like a pop-up book or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.73,0:03:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a card like it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toon World... what kind of card is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.68,0:04:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, when that thing appeared, Pegasus' black rabbit disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did your Dark Rabbit go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now all my cards have become Toon cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They now live here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't see them, they must be hiding somewhere in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, he's about to show himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Rabbit, attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toon Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dark Rabbit has gone back\N to hiding in the picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:05:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I forgot to tell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once Toon World is closed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no monsters are able to lay any damage to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun can't attack him back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set a card face-down, and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to be my turn, Kaiba boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Blue-Eyes White Dragon I got from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll play this card in Attack Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:06:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... my Blue-Eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.54,0:06:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of my monsters have become residents of Toon World.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it more lovable than before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.20,0:06:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.88,0:06:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba's Blue-Eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the power of Toon World.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes Toon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Rude Kaiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? I feel anger in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus... it seems you already know what cards are in my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, I'll discard my entire hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to play the first card I draw from my deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:07:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, even I won't know what it will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll play it on the field in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kaiba bastard's pretty much given up to resort to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.... I can kind of understand what Kaiba means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.44,0:07:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's betting everything on the card he'll draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.95,0:07:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba trusts in his deck with all his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.91,0:07:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine the burden he's shouldering to go this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've matured a lot, Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.21,0:07:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go! I'm betting everything on this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card I believed in....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.42,0:07:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To draw Blue-Eyes in this situation...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.44,0:07:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card Kaiba called with his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kaiba bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to admit it, but he's really a first-class Duelist!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus, you said you could feel my anger...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you what anger {\i1}really{\i0} is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fight with the real Blue-Eyes against the Toon Blue-Eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Toon World is unlike anything I've ever seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To draw another Blue-Eyes... you're truly a lucky boy, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing my proud monster\N into that disgusting thing...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you, Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.86,0:08:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oooohh nooo~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.80,0:08:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.21,0:08:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Stream!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It evaded the attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.89,0:09:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus' Blue-Eyes stretched out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funny Rabbit aired a total of 583 episodes on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In all of which the bad guy fired a total of 26000 bullets at the good guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And not a single one ever hit Funny Rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Toon World remains on my board...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,every card I play will become a Toon Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.51,0:09:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toons are the perfect form of being!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.85,0:09:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means he can't defeat any of the Toons!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard Pegasus...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he is the creator of Duel Monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.59,0:10:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,using that card is cheap!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, did you know about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... but those cards aren't sold to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one of each in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Original cards meant for Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making cards for himself is too dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba boy... you realized I could see your cards through your eyes so you abandoned your hand and drew from your deck...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.35,0:10:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But even that is useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When players assemble their decks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they memorize all their cards, even if only subconsciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.36,0:10:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In other words, I know every\N card assembled in your deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new page in Toon World!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.89,0:11:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Light-Attribute monster receives this and powers up by 500 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new page in Toon World?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.80,0:11:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chapter of your defeat has been written in Toon World.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Blue-Eyes Toon Dragon, receive the light's energy and power up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus' Toon Dragon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has more Attack Points than Kaiba's Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes Toon Dragon attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Stream!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic Card activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:11:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack Nullification!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.82,0:12:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Pegasus' attack was blocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.69,0:12:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course, I knew you had that Magic Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.88,0:12:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Attack Nullification is a one-time only card.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next turn, there's no way you'll block my Toon Dragon's attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If this continues, my Blue-Eyes will be killed by the Toon Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that happens, I have no chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.60,0:12:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mokuba... I'll stake our fate on this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.68,0:12:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.28,0:12:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spell of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spell of Darkness stops the enemy from moving
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.63,0:12:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and decreases their Attack down by 700 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.33,0:13:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There was only one card in Kaiba boy's deck that could defeat the Toon Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To draw that card now of all times...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Great...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even your Toon can't move once bound by the Spell of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Stream!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He defeated Pegasus' Toon Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto Kaiba.... you're very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't let you live as a pathetic Toon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've put you out of your misery...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.37,0:13:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kaiba boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I felt love for\N your Blue-Eyes in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As the Duel Monsters creator,\N I feel very complimented.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.95,0:14:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that love for your Blue-Eyes will be the trigger of your defeat. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.69,0:14:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card I've played... is the Dragon-Type Sealing Jar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Dragon-types will be sealed in this jar!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Sealing Jar gains the Defense Points of the dragon it absorbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.72,0:14:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn you Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.26,0:14:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to destroy that jug before he uses the second Blue-Eyes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A monster in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place this card Face down...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.15,0:15:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the Jar Genie in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the combo Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to revive the Blue-Eyes as your servant...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll turn it into a Toon to deliver the final blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.50,0:15:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ending will be very miserable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.67,0:15:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush that measly Jar Genie first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.14,0:15:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword Stalker the Avenger! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn that Jar Genie into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card Copy Cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can copy any you've played on the board!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.69,0:15:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card I'm going to copy is the Virus Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I infect Jar Genie with the virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus made the virus holder Jar Genie!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't attack, Kaiba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.29,0:16:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you say "attack", it can't be stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.82,0:16:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Virus Card destroys every monster in your deck with over 1500 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the Monsters in my Deck were destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.13,0:16:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your deck is made up almost entirely of over-powered Monsters with brute strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Kaiba's powerful deck to crumble this easily...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.22,0:16:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he's still got Life Points, he's got no cards left!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.94,0:16:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only card I've got left...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Resurrection of the Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use this card to revive Saggi the Dark Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I praise your ability to play out this game to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:17:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I should defeat that card on my next turn, I shall win!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Devil Box!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.65,0:17:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no cards left in your hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba boy, I presume you are aware of what it means to lose a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The loser loses {\i1}everything{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is precious to them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.14,0:17:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And even {\i1}themselves{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall suffer the same fate as Mokuba boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.52,0:18:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind Card!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.57,0:18:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your mind has now been sealed within this card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.12,0:18:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You will now eternally become my servant,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}forced to carry out my every bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.17,0:18:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The elder brother and younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.29,0:18:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two cards are this close,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet their souls are separated by what almost seems like infinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you'd have enjoyed a better meeting had you gone to the other world instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remove the corpse from my presence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba just ended up the same as Mokuba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:19:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-kun fought with his life on the line in order to save Mokuba-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's no different from us, trying to protect those important to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.05,0:19:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have {\i1}no{\i0} right to take away what's precious to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All that remains now is Yugi boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.19,0:19:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So you've shown yourself, other Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus! I'll defeat you with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.70,0:19:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi boy, if you desire to fight against me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you must win the tournament first.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.33,0:19:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'd better prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My anger won't submit until I've beaten you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.55,0:19:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The final tournament shall begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this very Duel Ring!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one of the four remaining Duelists shall earn the right to challenge me for eternal fame and glory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.81,0:20:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi boy... Even if you wield the Millennium Puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It is all but ineffective before my Millennium Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Allow me to prove this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(129,137)}"Preview"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi and the gang enjoy much needed relaxation and prepare for the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.13,0:20:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Pegasus' Mind Scan sure is suspicious, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! Isn't that a peephole?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be spying on the opponent's hand from that tower over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda! Bakura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go investigate that tower for Yugi and Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time! The Night Before the Finals! Pegasus' Secrets
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.96,0:21:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The flask shines bright
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}waiting in the Science Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By rubbing our cold hands together...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They will become warm
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.54,0:21:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It'll shower all over you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will support your lonely back
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An energy shower
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.38,0:21:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.04,0:22:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're surrounded by a ring of friendship
